Day 87: Ansible Install Package

Date: December 17, 2025
Overview
Automated package installation across multiple distributions.
Key Concepts Learned

Package module (yum, apt, dnf)
Distribution-specific handling
Package state management
Update and upgrade operations

Playbook
yaml- name: Install packages
  yum:
    name:
      - httpd
      - git
      - vim
    state: present
    update_cache: yes

Challenges Faced
Handling different package managers for different Linux distributions.

